column16: Jon Jay singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Skip Schumaker grounds out, second baseman Chris Nelson to first baseman Todd Helton.
Paul Janish flies out to left fielder Ryan Spilborghs.
Corky Miller lines out to shortstop Clint Barmes.
Miguel Tejada flies out to left fielder Ryan Spilborghs.
Nick Hundley homers (6) on a fly ball to left field.   Chris Denorfia scores.
James Loney grounds out, second baseman Jonathan Herrera to first baseman Todd Helton.
Matt Kemp singles on a line drive to left fielder Carlos Gonzalez.    Ryan Theriot scores.    Andre Ethier to 3rd.
